ok its been a while... i've been up to crazy shit... especially fight night which was AWESOME, kelly is my idol for being a nunja, not a typo haha. and i loved running past people like WHERE IS FIGHT NIGHT!!!... good times. umm then this weekend was cool, eddies house was fun with uber good food as usual. AND HAPPY MEALS WITH JO AND EMILY!... goood times haha... ummmmmmmmm... shit i lost my train of thought, maybe its been hijacked by terrorists... OMG I SHOULD BE A TERRORIST FOR HALLOWEEN... no! IM GONNA BE A NINJA! i love ninjas... but that is too cliche... A BUNNY NINJA!... YES I AM GOING TO BE A BUNNY NINJA!!! ok seriously i was gonna say something but i cant remember wat it was... screw it... I WROTE A ZOMBIE SONG!! haha i love zombies, and songs... so its like the best of both worlds... SOMEONE NEEDS TO COME UP WITH A CLEVER NAME FOR IT!

the year is 2010
i remember dooms day
we've been fighting since then
oh shit there's one behind you
BAM i blew off his head
what are we gonna do
we're fighting the undead

make sure you aim for the head 
but how can you kill them
when they're already dead

the walking dead are coming
and we cant stop them
everyone is running
this is never gonna end
every rot should be shot
if you were smart
cuz if not
they'll rip you apart

make sure you aim for the head 
but how can you kill them
when they're already dead

aim for the head, stop the undead
aim for the head, scatter their brains
aim for the head, stop the undead
aim for the head, scatter their brains

hahahahaha i crack myself up... so yea, fun times, name the song... im weird WOO!
later dudes and dudettes!

yea this weekend was sweet. matt and hilary came over, which was fuckin sweet. umm the game on friday was cool i guess, kelly's was definitely fun, thanks for having us over kelly belly :), umm so yea back to saturday, matt and hilary came over and we went to a haunted house then to steak and shake, fun times. then sunday i went to eddies... and this is where we kick it up a notch bitch. first we rode our bikes around the neighborhood and found guess wat... SHEEP, GOATS, AND CHICKENS!!!!... we even caught one of the chickens woo! then we threw nails into this house they're building and basically just destroyed shit lol, sucks for those guys. then we went back and had some of eddie's mom's awesome cooking which is making me fat haha, it was glorious. then the next day we went bike riding on the golf course and totally tore up the sand traps with our bikes it was hilarious. then we went frisbee golfing... yea haha we're sweet. and we found this black pipe at the construction site and so i got in it and rolled down these huge mounds of dirt, it was sooo much fun i wish we had a video camera. then we broke some more shit and left, listening to the tenacious d cd which is officially in the top ten of all cds ever made. so yea it was uber fun... well thats about it
-jake

consistency is not my thing... constant change in emotion warps my soul twisting my being... i dont kno how much more i can take... anger, hate, love, happiness, sadness trying to take over at the same time with the victor taking me in its grip... save me please...

RAGE!... i've missed this glorious feeling, 
let it grip me, consume me, and take me away
to a place where nothing matters but revenge, 
and i will have no pain again, only the joy 
of seeing your corpse, then this rage will 
completely destroy me and i will be gone, 
having finished my final task...
HATE!... and spite, you stir up these feelings
inside me, i think about you and i desire to
kill, hate comes from the tortured soul, and 
is passed on, and in me grows a hatred that
you cannot even begin to fathom, and will
be passed unto you in the form of my blade...
SADNESS... will take over me, as i gasp for
air, the adrenaline flowing through my body
is leaving me, and leaving behind a feeling of 
emptiness, now that the fire of my rage has been
put out, and my hatred has escaped into your corpse,
i have nothing left, and as was said in the fire, 
this rage has consumed me, off to quench my 
unquenchable thirst for blood, i go out into the
world, and will soon find my death...

yo ok i just got back from the true body project premiere and it was awesome. jess nolte was amazing up their totally owning at guitar... and those girls are so totally cool. and u kno it got me thinkin about how much im talkin to girls and i'll try to compliment them but they always end up finding things wrong with them to prove me wrong... its sad really. so im gonna take this moment to say that every girl i have the honor of calling my friend and even those i havent even met yet are totally amazing, beautiful, smart, and capable of anything and i mean every word. no more telling yourself your not any of those things because YOU ARE! if you dont believe it talk to me and i'll give u plenty of reasons why you are so great. i love you all. 
<3 jake

camping was amazing, me and eddie had the most fun you could ever have getting lost, then the playing with fire, the jokes, the chopping down trees, duct taping the sign, playing with hot embers the stars, jayme <3, it was incredible... but i need to get my fucking head straight, and i talked to jess for a while last night and she helped so much... THANKS JESS :)

this entry will describe quite possibly the greatest weekend of my life... ok so friday we were all gonna see the exorcism of emily rose, so i go pick up jayme and we head over to newport, fun trip thanks to my dads crazy driving haha "aw they suckered me in, u couldnt see the line from the highway, damnit"... so yea we get there and no one else is there so we call around and people are still on their way so me and jayme go ahead and get in line where marty meets up with us, and we all get our tickets and head to the movie. and the place is packed so we get these ok seat and then we get a phone call from liz and the movie is sold out! so me jayme and marty got to see it, and it was scary i'll say that lol. and i love being with jayme so that was awesome, then the night ended with us meeting up with everyone and meeting this dude in a band then we went home. great night. but then saturday was like the most perfect day ever. i went to jayme's house after renting sixteen candles, the dude at blockbuster looked at me like wtf? it was priceless. so anywho i get there and jayme's like let go "take apart" this broken ipod, which ended up with me taking a hammer to it several times, very satisfying i will say that. and i met mr. spider who is one cool spider. then we walked chance and zoey to her new house and walked around in there, its gonna be so cool when its done. then on the way back the dogs were way tired so jayme's mom came and picked us up. then we ordered pizza, and there was jones soda it was heavenly lol. and so we watched sixteen candles which to my surprise i enjoyed, crazy huh? maybe its cuz i was watching it with jayme :). then we went outside to lay on the roof of her batting cages thingy and look at the stars. it was awesome, we named one star ryan, and it was a retarded shooting star we think, dont ask haha, but ryan is cool. and so we were looking at the stars on the roof and i looked over at jayme and i'll say at that moment she was more beautiful than all the stars in the sky, and we had our first kiss right there on the roof under the stars, it was storybook... the way jayme makes me feel is amazing... so then we played with her crazy dog zoey, throwing sticks and wat not, and then we went inside and watched part of anger management haha... then the night had to end :(, i wish it could have lasted forever... and so that was the most amazing night ever with the most amazing person ever... wat a wonderful weekend

im quite possibly, along with matt lol, the weirdest person in the world... i mean i like screamo hardcore rock, and 90s love songs, i work out to be macho (which im not haha), but i think romantically and i like it, i pole vault and rock climb, i've wanted to be in the marines since age 10, i like explosions, but need my peace and quiet, im a pyro, i like to make everyone happy, even when i dont like seeing certain people happy haha, i'm not self centered most of the time, but i just typed this whole thing, i think women are cooler than men, but i love being a dude, i dont want much, but i would like a lot, i like shoot em up action movies, and i like whinne the pooh and i think im like tigger :), i still watch cartoons of course, i love cars but i cant drive, i want to be like other people, but i love being just me, im high on life, im rambling, but i've got a point, and i think jayme is the awesomest sexiest and everything else-est person ever :)... i am crazy and i kno it and im proud of it, it is the crowning achievement of my life... and i have friends who i love to death and probly do a lot of the things i just mentioned, SHOW YOUR PRIDE!

ok so im sitting here with matt at this pimp ass internet cafe with like 9 hours left in our trip and we are contemplating how fucking awesome it has been so i am going to write everything that has happened. ok so day one, we get here and go str8 to the beach, only to find out that there is no where to get a swimsuit for matt so we go home and tell my rents we're going to harbor town to get one for him and they go, you kno they wont have swimsuits up there and we go, yea we kno... but we'll go up there, be wrong, come back, and then u can take us to the mall. so we go up, find out we're wrong, get some coffee ice cream thing, go home then we go to the mall. at the mall we see this kick ass arcade and totally dominate the shoot em up games, like beat the whole freakin game. then walk further up to pac sun to get matt a swim suit, well they were 2 for 40 so we got 2 that were the same kind but different colors. then we realized there was no more stores there so we go back to pac sun and matt goes, dude u dont have any jeans do you, and im like no i dont wear jeans, so he goes dude if u buy urself some jeans i'll buy u a studded belt and so i am now wearing jeans for the first time since 6th grade woo haha, lemme tell ya its so hott. so umm matt ended up spendin like 180 dollars at pac sun and we were just laughing our asses off about it. then we went home and got our skimboards, and went up to the beach at like 6:30. so we get up there and skimboard all night, we were doin really good then we both tried a pop shove it and ate it haha. so umm that was just day one. day two we went to the beach and were swimming when these two total babes come up. so matts swims over like yo wats up. and so we met leah and melanie. spent some time hangin with them on the beach then we went back to our pool and being the geniuses we are decide to play tennis... in flip flops. first off the gate was locked and we didnt have the combo so i had to climb this like 10 foot fence and go on the other side to open it and we play in flip flops and this bug attacks matt and he cuts up his foot cuz we were running in flip flops. so umm we go home and then str8 to harbor town and get more coffee stuff and meet up with melanie and leah and chill with them up there umm yea that was day two. so day three we get up early and go to the beach and we're riding up with our pansy basket full of towels and shit and matt goes "oh look, it has a handle" and lifts the handle which detaches the basket and our shit goes flying everywhere it was hilarious. so we get to the beach an go skimboarding then come back for a bbq with the boeings. fun times haha, mitch is good at skimboarding i will say that. and umm im out of time i will finish later BYE!!! I MISS U ALL SOOO MUCH, PLEASE COMMENT!!
